title: Co-founder & Principal Program Officer
description: Strategic Leadership and Vision: I provide overall strategic leadership, vision, and operational oversight for a consultancy focused on advancing development solutions in Liberia and West Africa. I lead the firm’s core service areas, which include project management, strategic planning, public sector assessment, monitoring and evaluation, budgeting, and data analytics. My role involves enhancing the firm’s reputation as a trusted partner for government agencies, NGOs, donor organizations, and private sector clients. I ensure that our services address pressing socio-economic challenges and contribute to sustainable development outcomes ||Operational & Business Management: In this role, I oversee client engagement, business development, and project execution while fostering long-term partnerships through transparency, innovation, and high-quality service delivery. I manage diverse teams of consultants, aligning their expertise with client needs to ensure that projects are completed on time, within budget, and uphold the highest professional standards. Additionally, I lead compliance with legal and regulatory requirements, provide guidance on financial management and performance monitoring, and enhance the firm’s competitive position in the consultancy market through effective networking, thought leadership, and strategic promotion
